    <title>【C++ 学习】多线程</title>
    <link href="/2026/07/12/%E3%80%90C-%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E3%80%91%E5%A4%9A%E7%BA%BF%E7%A8%8B/"/>
    <url>/2026/07/12/%E3%80%90C-%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E3%80%91%E5%A4%9A%E7%BA%BF%E7%A8%8B/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="C-多线程"><a href="#C-多线程" class="headerlink" title="C++ 多线程"></a>C++ 多线程</h1><h2 id="1-多线程概念"><a href="#1-多线程概念" class="headerlink" title="1. 多线程概念"></a>1. 多线程概念</h2><p>在计算机中，多线程涉及以下概念:</p><ul><li>进程(Process): 是<strong>资源分配</strong>的最小单位。</li><li>线程(Thread): 是<strong>CPU 调度</strong>的最小单位。</li><li>多线程(Multi-thread): 是多核 CPU 的并行计算。</li></ul><p>在硬件条件下，由于单核 CPU 频率难以上升，为了运行效率，需要使用多线程，充分发挥多核 CPU 的能力。</p><p>多线程的好处:</p><ul><li>程序运行效率提高</li><li>避免程序运行阻塞</li></ul><p>但是由于异步执行的特性，多线程的缺点:</p><ul><li><strong>数据竞争(Data Race)</strong><br>当多个线程同时访问同一个数据时，可能会导致数据不一致的情况出现。</li><li><strong>竞态条件(Race Condition)</strong><br>程序执行的顺序是不确定的，可能会导致有依赖关系的的代码被随机错误地执行，极难调试。</li><li><strong>死锁(Deadlock)</strong><br>当多个线程互相等待对方的资源，造成互相等待，导致死锁。</li><li>性能下降<br>多线程的创建会导致线程切换的开销，使用不当降低了程序的性能。</li></ul><h2 id="2-多线程的实现"><a href="#2-多线程的实现" class="headerlink" title="2. 多线程的实现"></a>2. 多线程的实现</h2><p>C++ 在 C++11 引入了 <code>&lt;thread&gt;</code> 线程库，使得我们可以忽略不同平台的底层线程 API 差异。</p><p>实现细节:</p><ul><li><code>class std::thread</code> 为线程的封装类，包含了线程的生命周期管理等功能。<br>维护以下内容:<ul><li><strong>线程句柄(Thread Handle)</strong>: 操作系统中的线程标识符，用于 <code>join()</code> 和 <code>detach()</code>。</li><li><strong>线程栈(Thread Stack)</strong>: 操作系统分配的私有栈空间，用于存储线程的本地数据（可用 <code>ulimit -s</code> 查看大小）。</li><li><strong>TLS(Thread Local Storage)</strong>: 线程局部存储，用于存储线程的本地数据。</li></ul></li></ul><p>Warning: 线程不可复制，即 <code>thread(const thread&amp;) = delete;</code>，但可以使用移动语义</p><p>底层操作:</p><ul><li><strong>类型擦除(Type Erasure)</strong>: <code>std::thread</code> 为了接受所有可调用对象(lambda，函数对象，函数指针等)，会打包进 <code>std::function</code> 对象。</li><li><strong>构造函数拷贝&#x2F;移动参数</strong>: 正如上文，线程有私有的线程栈，需要将参数拷贝或移动到线程栈中（主要性能开销）。</li><li><strong>异常捕获</strong>: 底层入口函数会包裹一个 <code>try-catch</code> 块，用于调用 <code>std::terminate()</code>，防止程序崩溃。</li></ul><p>C++ 在 C++20 引入了 <code>std::jthread</code> ，可在析构时自动调用 <code>join()</code>，并且实现了<strong>协作式中断(Stop Token)</strong>，通过 <code>std::stop_token</code> 检查是否停止。</p><h2 id="3-多线程的使用"><a href="#3-多线程的使用" class="headerlink" title="3. 多线程的使用"></a>3. 多线程的使用</h2><ol><li>创建线程(<code>&lt;thread&gt;</code>)</li></ol><ul><li>语法: <code>std::thread t(func, args...);</code></li><li>参数:<ul><li><code>func</code>: 要执行的可调用对象。</li><li><code>args...</code>: 可调用对象的参数。</li></ul></li><li>细节:<ul><li>引用传递: 可以使用 <code>std::ref()</code> （位于 <code>&lt;functional&gt;</code>） 函数将对象引用传递给线程，优化性能。</li><li>生命周期: 创建后必须使用 <code>t.join()</code> （阻塞主线程直到结束） 或 <code>t.detach()</code> （分离线程后台运行），优先使用 <code>std::jthread</code>, <code>t.join()</code> 或 <code>RAII</code> 封装。</li></ul></li></ul><ol start="2"><li>互斥量(<code>&lt;mutex&gt;</code>)</li></ol><p>解决线程间的数据竞争问题。</p><ul><li>语法: <code>std::mutex mtx;</code></li><li>细节:<ul><li><code>mtx.lock()</code> 和 <code>mtx.unlock()</code> 用于加锁和解锁（Warning: 不建议使用）。</li><li><code>std::lock_guard&lt;std::mutex&gt; lock(mtx);</code>: <code>RAII</code> 的典范，用于自动加锁和解锁，在多个互斥量情况下容易死锁（推荐使用）。</li><li><code>std::unique_lock&lt;std::mutex&gt; lock(mtx);</code>: 给单个互斥量加锁，防止死锁（推荐使用）。</li><li><code>std::scoped_lock&lt;std::mutex&gt; lock(mtx);</code>: 给多个互斥量加锁，防止死锁（推荐使用）。</li></ul></li></ul><ol start="3"><li>原子操作(<code>&lt;atomic&gt;</code>)</li></ol><p>对互斥量的优化。</p><ul><li>语法: <code>std::atomic&lt;T&gt; var;</code></li><li>细节:<ul><li><code>var.load()</code> 读取当前变量值。</li><li><code>var.store(x)</code> 设置变量值为 <code>x</code>。</li><li>保证数据的原子性，无须加锁，性能更好。</li></ul></li></ul><p><strong><code>atomic_flag</code> 优化</strong></p><p><code>std::atomic_flag</code> 是 C++ 标准中唯一保证总是无锁(Lock-Free)的原子类型，不支持 <code>load</code> 和 <code>store</code> 操作，但可以使用 <code>clear</code> （清除为 false） 和 <code>test_and_set</code> （设置并返回旧值，设置为 true）和 <code>test()</code> （C++ 20, 返回当前值） 操作来实现原子操作，用于构建高性能的自旋锁(Spinlock)。</p><blockquote><p>自旋锁(Spinlock): 自旋(Spin)的线程不会进入休眠状态，而是进行空循环(Busy Waiting)，相比于互斥量(Mutex)，不涉及上下文切换(Context Switch)，在锁释放的极快时，自旋消耗的 CPU 可能远小于上下文切换的成本。</p></blockquote><p><strong>CAS 优化</strong></p><p>代码实例:</p><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cpp">std::atomic&lt;<span class="hljs-type">int</span>&gt; counter;<br><span class="hljs-comment">// ...</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (counter &gt; <span class="hljs-number">0</span>) &#123; <span class="hljs-comment">// 原子操作 1</span><br>    counter--;     <span class="hljs-comment">// 原子操作 2</span><br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>虽然 <code>atomic</code> 对于单个操作是原子的，但是多个操作不是原子的，例如上面的**检查-在执行(Check-then-act)**竞态条件。</p><p>为了解决此类问题，C++ 的答案为 <strong>Compare-and-Swap(CAS)</strong> 操作，提供了一个语义：“如果值等于预期值，就把它改成新值；否则就什么都不做。”。</p><p>C++ 定义了 <code>std::atomic::compare_exchange_strong()</code> 和 <code>std::atomic::compare_exchange_weak()</code> 函数实现，之所以有两个函数，是因为<code>strong</code> 严格保证原子性，而 <code>weak</code> 不严格，可能出现伪失败(Spurious Failure)。</p><p>在 x86&#x2F;x64 (CAS 架构) 上，提供了 CPU 指令 <code>LOCK CMPXCHG</code>，天然强指令，故 <code>strong</code> 和 <code>weak</code> 开销基本一致，而在 ARM&#x2F;PowerPC&#x2F;RISC-V (LL&#x2F;SC 架构) 上，CPU 不提供 <code>CMPXCHG</code>，而是使用 <strong>LL&#x2F;SC(Load-Link&#x2F;Store-Conditional)</strong>，操作是分离的，可能出现判断成功，但操作失败的情况，在此情况下 <code>weak</code> 性能强于 <code>strong</code>。</p><p>| 特性 | <code>strong</code> | <code>weak</code> |<br>| — | — |<br>| 原子性 | 严格保证 | 不严格，可能出现伪失败 |<br>| 开销 | 可能略慢 | 在 ARM 等架构更好 |<br>| 场景 | 单次逻辑判断 | 循环无锁判断 |</p><p>语法: <code>var.compare_exchange_{type}(expected, desired)</code></p><ul><li><code>expected</code>: 预期值</li><li><code>desired</code>: 新值</li></ul><p>代码修改:</p><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cpp">std::atomic&lt;<span class="hljs-type">int</span>&gt; counter&#123;<span class="hljs-number">1</span>&#125;;<br><br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> old_val = counter.<span class="hljs-built_in">load</span>();<br><span class="hljs-keyword">while</span> (<span class="hljs-literal">true</span>) &#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (old_val &lt;= <span class="hljs-number">0</span>) <span class="hljs-keyword">break</span>; <span class="hljs-comment">// 单原子，无耦合</span><br><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (counter.<span class="hljs-built_in">compare_exchange_weak</span>(old_val, old_val - <span class="hljs-number">1</span>)) &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">break</span>;<br>    &#125;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>内存序(Memory Order) 优化</strong></p><p>默认情况下，原子操作均使用 <code>std::memory_order_seq_cst</code> （顺序一致性），保证全局执行顺序。</p><ul><li><code>std::memory_order_relaxed</code>: 仅保证原子性，不保证指令顺序，编译器会乱序优化。</li><li><code>std::memory_order_acquire</code> &#x2F; <code>release</code>: 建立同步关系。Release 保证此操作之前的所有内存写入对执行 Acquire 的线程在该操作之后可见，建立先行发生关系(Happens-Before)。</li><li><code>std::memory_order_seq_cst</code>: 默认，最严格，保证指令顺序，但性能开销大。</li><li><code>std::memory_order_acq_rel</code>: 用于**读-改-写(Read-Modify-Write)**操作，在读取时为 <code>acquire</code>，写入时为 <code>release</code>。</li></ul><p>类似 <code>compare_exchange_weak</code> ，修改内存序对 ARM 等架构优化较大，对 x86&#x2F;x64 影响较小。</p><ol start="4"><li>线程间通信(<code>Inter-Thread Communication</code>)</li></ol><p>在多线程中，为了等待特定条件，需要使用 <code>std::condition_variable</code>，严禁使用 <code>while</code>。</p><p>条件变量(<code>condition_variable</code>)</p><p>用于线程挂起与唤醒，实现线程同步。</p><ul><li>语法: <code>std::condition_variable cv;</code></li><li>依赖: 必须配合 <code>std::unique_lock&lt;std::mutex&gt;</code> 使用。</li><li>调用:<ul><li><code>cv.wait(lock, predicate);</code>: 若不满足条件则挂起并释放锁，直到满足条件为止。</li><li><code>cv.notify_one();</code> &#x2F; <code>cv.notify_all();</code>: 唤醒一个或所有线程。</li></ul></li></ul><p>Warning: 操作系统可能在无信号条件下唤醒线程，建议 <code>wait</code> 搭配 <strong>lambda 谓词</strong> 使用。</p><h2 id="4-线程辅助库"><a href="#4-线程辅助库" class="headerlink" title="4. 线程辅助库(&lt;this_thread&gt;)"></a>4. 线程辅助库(<code>&lt;this_thread&gt;</code>)</h2><ol><li><code>std::this_thread::sleep_for</code></li></ol><ul><li>语法: <code>std::this_thread::sleep_for(std::chrono::duration&lt;Rep, Period&gt;);</code></li><li>参数:<ul><li><code>std::chrono::duration&lt;Rep, Period&gt;</code>: 时长，Rep 是算数类型，Period 是时长单位，为 <code>std::ratio&lt;Num, Den</code> 类型，表示每 <code>Num</code> 秒有 <code>Den</code> 个单位。常用的 <code>milliseconds</code>, <code>seconds</code> 都是 <code>Duration</code> 的别名(alias)。</li></ul></li><li>作用: 让出 CPU 时间片，挂起线程，直到时间耗尽再被唤醒。</li></ul><ol start="2"><li><code>std::this_thread::yield</code></li></ol><ul><li>语法: <code>std::this_thread::yield();</code></li><li>作用: 主动让出 CPU 时间片，挂起线程，直到下次被调度，通常与自旋锁一起使用。</li></ul><ol start="3"><li><code>std::this_thread::get_id</code></li></ol><ul><li>语法: <code>std::this_thread::get_id();</code></li><li>作用: 获取当前线程 ID，方便调试。</li></ul><h2 id="5-代码实践"><a href="#5-代码实践" class="headerlink" title="5. 代码实践"></a>5. 代码实践</h2><h3 id="5-1-线程生命管理-std-jthread"><a href="#5-1-线程生命管理-std-jthread" class="headerlink" title="5.1 线程生命管理(std::jthread)"></a>5.1 线程生命管理(<code>std::jthread</code>)</h3><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cpp"><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span> <span class="hljs-string">&lt;iostream&gt;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span> <span class="hljs-string">&lt;stop_token&gt;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span> <span class="hljs-string">&lt;thread&gt;</span></span><br><br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">worker</span><span class="hljs-params">(</span></span><br><span class="hljs-params"><span class="hljs-function">    std::stop_token st)</span> </span>&#123;  <span class="hljs-comment">// 若想让 jthread 通知退出，需要把参数列表第一个传入 std::stop_token</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">while</span> (!st.<span class="hljs-built_in">stop_requested</span>()) &#123;<br>        std::cout &lt;&lt; <span class="hljs-string">&quot;working...&quot;</span> &lt;&lt; std::endl;<br>        std::this_thread::<span class="hljs-built_in">sleep_for</span>(std::chrono::<span class="hljs-built_in">seconds</span>(<span class="hljs-number">1</span>));<br>    &#125;<br>    std::cout &lt;&lt; <span class="hljs-string">&quot;Cleanup and exit.&quot;</span> &lt;&lt; std::endl;<br>&#125;<br><br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title">main</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span> </span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-comment">// 创建即运行，析构自动 join</span><br>    <span class="hljs-function">std::jthread <span class="hljs-title">t</span><span class="hljs-params">(worker)</span></span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="5-2-互斥量与死锁预防-std-mutex-std-scoped-lock"><a href="#5-2-互斥量与死锁预防-std-mutex-std-scoped-lock" class="headerlink" title="5.2 互斥量与死锁预防(std::mutex, std::scoped_lock)"></a>5.2 互斥量与死锁预防(<code>std::mutex</code>, <code>std::scoped_lock</code>)</h3><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cpp"><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span> <span class="hljs-string">&lt;functional&gt;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span> <span class="hljs-string">&lt;iostream&gt;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span> <span class="hljs-string">&lt;mutex&gt;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span> <span class="hljs-string">&lt;thread&gt;</span></span><br><br>std::mutex mtx1;<br>std::mutex mtx2;<br><br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">safe_swap</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-type">int</span>&amp; a, <span class="hljs-type">int</span>&amp; b)</span> </span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-function">std::scoped_lock <span class="hljs-title">lock</span><span class="hljs-params">(mtx1, mtx2)</span></span>;<br>    std::<span class="hljs-built_in">swap</span>(a, b);<br>&#125;<br><br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title">main</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span> </span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-type">int</span> a = <span class="hljs-number">1</span>, b = <span class="hljs-number">2</span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-function">std::thread <span class="hljs-title">t1</span><span class="hljs-params">(safe_swap, std::ref(a), std::ref(b))</span></span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-function">std::thread <span class="hljs-title">t2</span><span class="hljs-params">(safe_swap, std::ref(a), std::ref(b))</span></span>;<br>    t<span class="hljs-number">1.</span><span class="hljs-built_in">join</span>();<br>    t<span class="hljs-number">2.</span><span class="hljs-built_in">join</span>();<br>    std::cout &lt;&lt; a &lt;&lt; <span class="hljs-string">&quot; &quot;</span> &lt;&lt; b &lt;&lt; std::endl;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="5-3-原子操作与自旋锁-std-atomic-flag"><a href="#5-3-原子操作与自旋锁-std-atomic-flag" class="headerlink" title="5.3 原子操作与自旋锁(std::atomic_flag)"></a>5.3 原子操作与自旋锁(<code>std::atomic_flag</code>)</h3><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cpp"><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span> <span class="hljs-string">&lt;atomic&gt;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span> <span class="hljs-string">&lt;thread&gt;</span></span><br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">SpinLock</span> &#123;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">private</span>:<br>    std::atomic_flag flag = ATOMIC_FLAG_INIT; <span class="hljs-comment">// 初始化为清除状态</span><br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span>:<br>    <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">lock</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span> </span>&#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">while</span> (flag.<span class="hljs-built_in">test_and_set</span>(std::memory_order_acquire)) &#123;<br>            std::this_thread::<span class="hljs-built_in">yield</span>();<br>        &#125;<br>    &#125;<br>    <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">unlock</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span> </span>&#123; flag.<span class="hljs-built_in">clear</span>(std::memory_order_release); &#125;<br>&#125;;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="5-3-CAS-高性能无锁循环-std-atomic"><a href="#5-3-CAS-高性能无锁循环-std-atomic" class="headerlink" title="5.3 CAS 高性能无锁循环(std::atomic)"></a>5.3 CAS 高性能无锁循环(<code>std::atomic</code>)</h3><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cpp"><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span> <span class="hljs-string">&lt;atomic&gt;</span></span><br><br>std::atomic&lt;<span class="hljs-type">int</span>&gt; counter&#123;<span class="hljs-number">100</span>&#125;;<br><br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">atomic_decrement</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span> </span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-type">int</span> old_val = counter.<span class="hljs-built_in">load</span>();<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">while</span> (!counter.<span class="hljs-built_in">compare_exchange_weak</span>(old_val, old_val - <span class="hljs-number">1</span>)) &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (old_val &lt;= <span class="hljs-number">0</span>) &#123;<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">break</span>;<br>        &#125;<br>    &#125;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="5-4-线程间通信"><a href="#5-4-线程间通信" class="headerlink" title="5.4 线程间通信"></a>5.4 线程间通信</h3><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cpp"><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span> <span class="hljs-string">&lt;condition_variable&gt;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span> <span class="hljs-string">&lt;iostream&gt;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span> <span class="hljs-string">&lt;mutex&gt;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span> <span class="hljs-string">&lt;queue&gt;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span> <span class="hljs-string">&lt;thread&gt;</span></span><br><br>std::queue&lt;<span class="hljs-type">int</span>&gt; q;<br>std::mutex mtx;<br>std::condition_variable cv;<br><br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">consumer</span><span class="hljs-params">(std::stop_token st)</span> </span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-function">std::unique_lock&lt;std::mutex&gt; <span class="hljs-title">lock</span><span class="hljs-params">(mtx)</span></span>;<br>    cv.<span class="hljs-built_in">wait</span>(lock, [] &#123; <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> !q.<span class="hljs-built_in">empty</span>(); &#125;);<br><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (st.<span class="hljs-built_in">stop_requested</span>()) &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span>;<br>    &#125;<br><br>    <span class="hljs-type">int</span> val = q.<span class="hljs-built_in">front</span>();<br>    q.<span class="hljs-built_in">pop</span>();<br>    std::cout &lt;&lt; val &lt;&lt; std::endl;<br>&#125;<br><br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">producer</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> val)</span> </span>&#123;<br>    &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-function">std::lock_guard&lt;std::mutex&gt; <span class="hljs-title">lock</span><span class="hljs-params">(mtx)</span></span>;<br>        q.<span class="hljs-built_in">push</span>(val);<br>    &#125;<br>    cv.<span class="hljs-built_in">notify_one</span>();<br>&#125;<br><br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title">main</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span> </span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-function">std::jthread <span class="hljs-title">t1</span><span class="hljs-params">(consumer)</span></span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-function">std::jthread <span class="hljs-title">t2</span><span class="hljs-params">(producer, <span class="hljs-number">100</span>)</span></span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="5-5-内存序同步-std-memory-order"><a href="#5-5-内存序同步-std-memory-order" class="headerlink" title="5.5 内存序同步(std::memory_order)"></a>5.5 内存序同步(<code>std::memory_order</code>)</h3><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cpp"><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span> <span class="hljs-string">&lt;atomic&gt;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span> <span class="hljs-string">&lt;thread&gt;</span></span><br><br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> data = <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br>std::atomic&lt;<span class="hljs-type">bool</span>&gt; ready&#123;<span class="hljs-number">0</span>&#125;;<br><br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">producer</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span> </span>&#123;<br>    data = <span class="hljs-number">42</span>;<br>    ready.<span class="hljs-built_in">store</span>(<span class="hljs-literal">true</span>, std::memory_order_release);<br>&#125;<br><br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">consumer</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span> </span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">while</span> (!ready.<span class="hljs-built_in">load</span>(std::memory_order_acquire)) &#123;<br>        std::this_thread::<span class="hljs-built_in">yield</span>();<br>    &#125;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
